## macOS
.DS_Store

## Xcode user data
**/xcuserdata/
*.xcuserstate
*.xcscmblueprint

## Xcode 26 auto-generates a duplicate workspace-level scheme next to the
## project-level one under RideVerse.xcodeproj/xcshareddata/. Ignore the
## workspace copy — project-level is the source of truth.
RideVerse.xcworkspace/xcshareddata/

## Xcode build output
DerivedData/
build/

## Swift Package Manager
.build/
.swiftpm/
Packages/*/Packages/
Packages/*/.build/
Packages/*/.swiftpm/
# Package.resolved — keep committed for reproducible builds (uncomment to ignore instead)
# **/Package.resolved

## Obsidian — keep vault config shared, ignore workspace state
.obsidian/workspace.json
.obsidian/workspaces.json
.obsidian/appearance.json
.obsidian/core-plugins.json

